  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지 소량 인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57984fa-13c7-40f9-8dfc-3ba3a4169eb8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2d0493b0-a8bd-41f9-ab36-bdbefebc24e8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4909dc42-623e-4e8a-a71d-312831fccb16\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9155cf59-6521-455b-a078-10ab77f1ac45\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e9126e85-f377-43f5-a255-00d9499ae707\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7f3954e9-77d1-49b2-91be-bba5fe4edc3e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-99e893dc-6bb2-424c-9cb2-b3a4a4afcfd6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>슬리브(sleeve)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3b1f7a68-ef7c-4328-8296-2cfc30acfa45\" style=\"color:#555555;\">라는 영어의 뜻은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d6e68b4a-9e0a-423a-9980-c22ace9e037b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b7482fea-cd38-4a0c-a376-e90e31e5c12d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기계 부의를 씌우는 보호관이라는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8c3a236a-e354-48cd-863e-69953e61a0e7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f4a7eb7-9554-4209-a124-e8c15fee3d20\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의미나 소매를 뜻합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b11c0896-a8ad-4fb8-a0aa-948a67031140\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-98dc45d6-5bc4-4a65-9019-7c38287af93f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f455271b-0cbc-4306-8ec9-dc534d71536e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28454071-5bd2-411a-b60f-2933628b5928\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품을 씌워서 포장한다는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8b6154bf-8d40-425d-a338-083f8182ab74\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3c4b87e-8d5e-4981-9b39-0272668fd533\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의미에서 슬리브 또는 슬라이드 박스로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-14b23edf-e7b3-4187-962f-21cf2141fd39\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4eda1a5e-63b9-4694-bac1-4d62674eccbb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">불립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-674c866c-b916-45c8-a1d4-4970fa857a70\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b2f27dcf-d29f-40a0-8026-00ad03ba1c32\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2dce8f7b-3c58-42ae-a139-95f9528816ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9d699362-e86d-4bee-a9b9-b8d60fcf0a7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>슬라이드(Slide)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f69ad647-2502-49ee-ac9c-1fc17c763a75\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-480410d8-702a-4818-8f79-b63cdb1d8bd2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-32adb402-ca6d-4fa4-86dd-117afc101d79\" style=\"color:#555555;\">미끄러지는 뜻으로 제품의 겉면을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d86c06f3-e1b6-4032-9ec2-327a28e6d975\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-141137e4-b536-4e09-a127-79e12fcdafe5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">미끄러지듯이 밀고 댕겨서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b8e59044-632f-4841-b7de-fbe020c240b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-963ff1ea-7dde-4323-ac0f-c656fd234885\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보호하는 표지가 있다는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5de1f43c-a841-44a9-a1c6-92b29c232b8d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e71abcc3-7fda-44a1-8f11-0388598fae4c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그런 의미에서 붙여진 말인듯합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d04890e7-6bb9-4c02-b430-d9d3a03cccfb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b7f9bf9-8a8a-4e7a-9eb8-545c1b89ed7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-334fe3c2-1610-4584-8b86-7482c8be0bda\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6e5e28f3-85e8-44cd-a4b0-833b9bd44977\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 모두 도무송(톰슨)이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cdeecec3-0784-41a2-a75e-874326d4e66c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fcce1ebe-8c5d-4467-82a7-ba0db23d42ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2형태가 들어가고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c4492a6e-f064-4eab-9b8b-a627e85b4108\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8419735f-04b9-4622-8d19-7d4b5082d21d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내부와 외곽 씌워지는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-329c8cec-1258-4002-996f-f27f7d9e891d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3f38d20a-e078-4e95-8acb-981356688de7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">부분의 두 가지 종류로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8ec54960-6a4b-46e9-8adc-14e4595360f3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b0a8dff1-3623-44c4-a6b0-0c30bbb57c8e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">나눠집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb3bb856-23c6-4848-94fa-64caaf12f7db\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f98704aa-e4a2-4aeb-ac6e-dfab9dc54384\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-caf1ff59-a6e8-480c-bbc7-3b3309058ba2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f748167f-fd2e-42e4-8562-5ed5891361e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 안에는 종이나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2170a98f-4e62-4cd3-9e06-c2f9d21d14a6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e88c88a0-f831-4d0a-8f37-4819cffff418\" style=\"color:#555555;\">포맥스, pp등의 형태로 패드를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-af616c98-15cf-42b5-b2d5-171c5b4f0cef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f77c039e-b82a-4d39-aee6-9610f8b7c8c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만들어 제품을 보호하거나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f37dc354-4df4-4ecb-80b6-b962ce9e8b8a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2c866cb-8a4b-4d43-9b6c-0d6b97271fda\" style=\"color:#555555;\">흔들리지 않도록</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-199a6aa9-2eb0-49b9-9782-e3029d11a17a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03d9a0c7-989e-4d8e-8be1-b05ce0a3c1a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96eb7be0-786a-4094-bc5b-27933a099c06\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/001.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-780ab5ef-f1b4-4fda-ad90-fe160f2eef34\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca2ccfff-dddc-489f-9289-6b8c80777c28\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b5a86a0f-b8da-4584-b7e7-b7a3ea235904\" style=\"\">슬리브 상자는 제작 과정이 복잡합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3d61204d-69d6-4f87-b933-7273f16da6ac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-018347fe-50f3-4a56-981e-25577362d0c9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-55997357-815f-4c3b-ae5d-3036cc2f2d8f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자와는 달리 슬리브 상자는 합지를 할 수도 있고 하나의 두꺼운 종이로 제작이 가능합니다. 물론 더 튼튼하게 만들기 위해 합지로 작업이 된다면 비용이 많이 들고 소량 생산은 불가능해집니다. 그렇기 때문에 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7e03b03d-f1a4-4bcf-8b93-ccbf5b89ebb6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>슬리브, 슬라이드 상자를 선택하실 때는 전문가와 제품과 내용에 따라 조언을 받고 제작하는 것이 중요</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5673e5ee-8131-47eb-9906-ee510d29f3e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-983e99fc-7501-4920-b2a4-22115eb56c7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be150857-8d22-4aff-83a2-9e512ac189bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be3d3f80-daa9-41dc-8796-9ae8fd13e48b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ed7b1c1-bd8b-4ed5-9788-07a3fb02729e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 방향과 안에 들어가는 패드의 목형, 그리고 슬라이드 외지가 헐겁거나 빡빡하지 않게 작업되는 것이 슬리브 상자의 핵심이라고 볼 수 있습니다. 이런 이유로 반드시 사이즈에 대한 정확한 검증이 필요하고 또한 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-44d95d20-0efc-430c-bcdf-d4d399c585f7\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>비용이 들더라도 샘플을 만들어 미리 맞춰보는 것도 중요</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-10c4b258-2f9c-46a4-bb8d-37185b3c23ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a8c24286-da76-436d-8a88-d5c76ae8f333\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b45e135-14b1-4b17-b8bf-96999d1309c6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f9753a5-c934-4e62-94ef-cf0572f78403\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-07f9433f-75bc-4fbb-9f91-5f49240405e7\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>슬리브 상자의 용도</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-342e5996-42f6-4dca-a362-61c5c4d956df\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-11fbfd6e-72ad-4b45-acf1-1f1b236ff426\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ab6c71f-c20e-4e0b-acf0-aaac2ccf3448\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc51bbac-5e9b-4929-9ae8-635e0fa8eb53\" style=\"color:#555555;\">슬리브 상자의 용도는 다양하게 활용되고 있습니다. 2개의 제품을 하나로 묶어 판매하는 경우 사용되기도 하고 제일 많이 사용되는 고급 수제 구두의 포장재로도 많이 이용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3832378e-3b33-4168-8a61-562f566be125\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-316c2be9-87e2-48c3-be1b-da238509822c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5765a4ab-2c62-4e57-b881-aa5bd9a6685b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3d7efa9a-1bb3-494d-9ef6-1178801289ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 선물용 이벤트로 제품을 여러 가지 담아 그 안에 칼선을 만들고 슬리브로 표지를 감싸는 형태로 제작이 많이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6d18e46-f824-44db-8efc-e52e7aea6601\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d43c32d5-6240-402f-991e-6e0992146c3e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-8f4ea4f9-a9f7-4c39-88ad-b4767e5c2f1f\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3015c50-4c7f-4f6f-aba7-8cad3c9188eb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2adcf37-d7e8-4016-a41c-01e87a89d58d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df1b87ff-66cb-45ef-97b8-f2391f9e5ce2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 창문을 뚫어 안의 내용물을 보이도록 구성할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0a4b32d-3467-4a19-a672-68bf05593ba9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5017c425-23aa-4122-a769-4181ec1924ab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b64c1bbd-f279-4b55-9bad-4a5d7c75b943\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1ac9504-e1d7-4d83-aab0-3d938e9729aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">슬리브 박스가 아닌 경우는 띠지라는 표현을 많이 쓰는데 이는 제품을 끼워서 내용물에 대한 설명을 표시하는 용도로 많이 사용됩니다. 이 경우는 박스 형태라기보다는 띠지 형태로 이야기하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2f6c2962-e584-4cf2-a152-91ed90da8d1d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-36be7402-297b-44ee-8882-75414611fe07\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-51b557d7-702f-4830-b46d-866c62f7e7ad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-799728f1-30f8-4733-b650-806ba9ae3317\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이처럼 우리 같은 인쇄인도 인쇄 용어나 일반적인 용어의 차이로 인해 서로의 소통이 어렵고 잘못 진행되는 경우가 허다합니다. 우리는 이 견적을 이렇게 이해하고 몇 분 또는 몇 시간을 말했지만 정작 나중에는 다른 상품을 이야기할 때 허탈감마저 듭니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-068d874e-ec0e-4717-b8ae-63708c5d3581\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c0b6337-ee55-4d7b-8d34-9b43d3b8a331\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a9cc2292-4879-4479-9a8f-95587dcad9db\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-10725267-18bc-4da8-9af9-7a2cc2bbed3f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그러므로 가장 좋은 방법은 말보다 또는 글보다 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6c778292-fb7e-4271-8cdf-7746c7ce06eb\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>만들고 싶은 이미지를 보여주는 것</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7eece840-d3de-4805-a6c2-298c51a0092e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 이것처럼 확실한 방법은 또 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-091fbae3-883a-4b93-9de6-390ae880d3ba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e18866d1-b782-4d3c-8a46-f786966f8156\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-69b6095c-a43d-44ac-b122-182ab58021a5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d84db48a-c6e7-42e9-a467-121472115971\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-12a9c80d-0fd4-4f1c-9deb-e32f40fc5078\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내부 인쇄면에 로고를 각인시킬 수 있고 아니면 인쇄 없이 깔끔하게 마감할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc2ad92b-d1e0-445e-bfa9-f447fbab2387\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5d93b17f-e94a-4b58-8e25-ac3c503c9f46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-252b6dbb-1abb-492c-b834-0a9c007ba5f7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5d8daba0-9afb-444f-b60b-c55b1477ba28\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-64807d7a-a5ef-4ac9-9eb1-3940fdce37c4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223766200224/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0e9854fc-b676-4668-b502-181cc8f3c565\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95d0a200-8302-43db-b065-2eb120cccd21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5b1c172a-6361-4aa2-ab95-2da3398bfbf0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">슬라이드 외부 표지 부분은 인쇄를 하는 경우가 대부분이지만 보통의 경우 인쇄 없이 형압이나 박인쇄로 포인트만 주고 작업할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d384b8e0-f4b3-475d-8f59-938259d0776b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5a098cc0-b162-42dc-8f5f-aea948fcac61\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-abdd6529-fa4e-4ef6-b73f-1ba0733a4ae9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-27e4b52b-958c-4442-84e4-96a142728eff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다양한 인쇄 방법이나 후공정 작업이 궁금하신 분은 언제든 문의하시고 연락 주세요. 저희가 아니더라도 패키지는 복잡한 공정으로 작업 진행이 되므로 전문가와 상의 후에 작업되도록 하기 바랍니다. 그래야 사고를 사전에 예방할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8db5b1a8-8b1b-4dc7-9277-b68f06630788\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b75d63ed-7d33-420c-878d-2143262e2e23\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line3\" id=\"SE-3581b0ba-e3c2-4a77-9c87-b9e6eb05c016\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line3 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-35f2f44d-1d26-452c-b248-867c1db37b35\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a9a238b-d5bf-422a-b717-3704cd57b5b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9389fa8f-7cfc-4655-afb7-423778025cee\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주문사양 정리</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aa68cf64-691f-4281-84c3-6522f22099a3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cff8e6a2-c1ae-427b-8be5-0ed2ed9f5ba3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af26625d-c8d7-495e-ad29-be0e47b0d776\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70a5aea6-ebeb-4163-98a2-79d61dba4b4b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">주문 수량은 제작방법에 따라 다르지만 보통의 경우 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6cdbf616-b8fc-41c0-a82b-2eb48d61b2ab\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>기본이 500</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9eeb2e59-d588-46a2-a1c7-41ab5de89740\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">개입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96ba5cfe-0197-46f7-8c6c-02c2f46000ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-570d32ab-618b-4786-86ee-8fd3a82a0f06\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">샘플 출력은 가능한 사이즈가 있지만 샘플이 불가능하거나 비용이 너무 많이 발생되는 경우도 있습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4788c5ce-1d80-4a61-902d-16de22c84042\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>전문가와 상의</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba6927d2-26be-479f-bbe6-aae8a7aa63d7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">하세요.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40b93df9-fd62-4be8-a813-d691772b3965\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3cea19d1-ce1e-49c3-b55b-1209fd617927\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>제품을 사전에 받고 칼선을 만드는 것이 중요</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3a87c384-6260-4370-b3d4-bd82ad4ed057\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">합니다. 슬리브는 사이즈가 틀리면 완성도에서 현격한 차이를 발생하는 제품입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d3819f12-0d68-4936-b439-dcd26e3e2dc3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0463c157-22d0-44cf-ae41-8d311b92af0e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">디자인도 조언해 드립니다. 제품의 성격이나 특징에 따라 정교한 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9b81b7c9-67fb-4b67-81d4-c082c648a619\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>디자인 지원이 가능</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4484ace5-c9f4-4733-991a-9a0777db0899\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-32aa28bc-bf31-4530-8dfb-b182b427a342\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-045584c8-d211-4891-ab4c-0b635eebadde\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>납기를 반드시 체크</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e68cad50-3319-48fc-af35-352f3970442e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">하시기 바랍니다. 슬리브는 납기가 기본적으로는 오래 걸리는 인쇄물입니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5089101e-0d4e-4f73-97b1-03c62c0e375e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75c8f7ac-b72d-424f-afc9-0a335ab8b1ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}